title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 10: Duncan Trussell
description:
Thanks for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat!!! This episode my guest is the one and only Duncan Trussell. On this episode we discuss....
1) Stand Up in NYC
2)Fascism
3)Wikileaks
4)The Deep State
5)World War 3
6) Just Love!
